Like and comment the tutorials you’d like to see from me! I’m using less than 20 products so I can quickly throw myself together each morning before my kids wake up! 
http://liketk.it/2TTs9 #liketkit @liketoknow.it 

•CC Cream - shade light medium
•TARTE Shape Tape - shade fair 
•Bronzer - shade natural
•Brow Pomade - shade blonde
•Tinted Brow Gel - shade dark blonde
•Build your own shadow pallet - M600 Matte Oat + M535 Matte Pink Brown
•Sugar Rush Liquid Lipstick - Cake Pop

node.text: Our Logan girl started 2nd grade today! How did we get here so fast?! I’m SO proud of her - she is kind, nurturing, warm, inclusive and so much fun! I’m so thankful to be your momma! 💛 also I can’t believe she’s almost as tall as me 😆

node.text: We made it home! It was such a fun trip with the family. We officially walked 33 miles in Disney 😆 it’s been a long time since I’ve been this sore haha. @troyleehunt and I decided to do a Disney trip for this months giveaway! We want to gift someone whether it’s a family/couple/or just a group of friends with a 3 night stay at the Grand California Disney hotel - flights - and park hopper tickets + some spending money ($4000 trip) it’s easy to enter just follow @troyleehunt + like and comment below. We will close and pick someone aug 13th. I can’t wait!!!!
